version_description: this will be the first and actual bar chord version
All previous versions have incorrect chords in Bridge and incorrect lyrics.
This one includes corrected chords throughout but specifically in the verses and the bridge.  Also includes the correct intro.
There are only two chords to this song. Other contributions have as many as four chords and over complicate what's really a very simple song.
This is based off of version 2. I was playing it and realized some of the chords sounded a bit off. imo this sounds a lot more like the actual song.
